<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Play Framework on 仕麟的博客</title><link>https://edward40.com/tags/play-framework/</link><description>Recent content in Play Framework on 仕麟的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 23 May 2015 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://edward40.com/tags/play-framework/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Play Framework項目初始化</title><link>https://edward40.com/posts/play-framework/</link><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://edward40.com/posts/play-framework/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://edward40.com/posts/play-framework/play.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Play Framework項目初始化" />&lt;h2 id="安裝-activator">安裝 Activator&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>先下載&lt;a class="link" href="http://www.typesafe.com/community/core-tools/activator-and-sbt" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Activator&lt;/a>
解壓到&lt;code>D:\Program Files\activator-1.3.2&lt;/code>
將&lt;code>D:\Program Files\activator-1.3.2&lt;/code>加到環境變量 Path 中
在你的項目目錄中執行以下命令，驗證是否安裝成功&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">activator -help
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="創建-play-項目">創建 Play 項目&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">activator new demo play-java
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> demo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">activator
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="安裝-eclipse-插件">安裝 Eclipse 插件&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="http://scala-ide.org/download/current.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Scala IDE&lt;/a>
在 Eclipse 中 Install New Software 增加宰割 Update Site，記得安裝 Play Support&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="創建-eclipse-項目">創建 Eclipse 項目&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">eclipse with-source&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="跑起來看看">跑起來看看&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">run
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>在瀏覽器中打開&lt;a class="link" href="http://localhost:9000" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>http://localhost:9000&lt;/a>，項目就跑起來了 ╰(￣ ▽ ￣)╮&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>